reviewText: Such a joyful DVD... I love watching the kittens play; it's like I am right there with them. If you love cats but can't have one because of allergies or housing arrangements, this is the next best thing! A great gift for any cat lover!
Fantastic, super funny, the production was very good, all the animals had cute names and the music was great. My kids ask to watch it constantly. Best baby-sitter i ever hired.
